# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:34
translate spanish hwb_s23_6b850b2e:

    # "‘Sleeping on it’ is supposed to help you with tough decisions, or with big changes, but that’s hard when you can’t pass out in the first place."
    "Se supone que \"dormir sobre ello\" ayuda con decisiones difíciles o grandes cambios, pero es difícil cuando ni siquiera puedes quedarte dormida."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:36
translate spanish hwb_s23_1e530efb:

    # "Thoughts of Marina, and of Gramps, and of things changing, and of things staying the same all brewed together to keep me awake just like the coffee is right now."
    "Pensamientos sobre Marina, y sobre el Abuelo, y sobre las cosas que cambian, y sobre las que se quedan igual, todo se mezcló para mantenerme despierta, justo como el café ahora."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:38
translate spanish hwb_s23_f38e93dc:

    # "When I got up this morning, the first thing I felt was surprise that I’d managed to fall asleep at all."
    "Cuando me levanté esta mañana, lo primero que sentí fue sorpresa de haber logrado quedarme dormida."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:40
translate spanish hwb_s23_91a63f7e:

    # "The three hours I got must have snuck up on me."
    "Las tres horas que dormí debieron haberme tomado por sorpresa."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:42
translate spanish hwb_s23_9798f90d:

    # "I drain another cup of coffee. Number four, and the last one from this pot. I dump another few scoops of grounds into the coffeemaker and start a new batch."
    "Termino otra taza de café. La número cuatro, y la última de esta jarra. Echo unas cucharadas más de café molido en la cafetera y preparo una nueva tanda."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:44
translate spanish hwb_s23_31797c20:

    # "I got to see the sunrise, which even I usually sleep through. Out here in the middle of nowhere, with no light pollution, the sky was vivid; shards of jagged pink tearing into the blue."
    "Pude ver el amanecer, que incluso yo normalmente me pierdo durmiendo. Aquí, en medio de la nada, sin contaminación lumínica, el cielo era vívido; fragmentos de rosa irregular rasgando el azul."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:46
translate spanish hwb_s23_e3090afb:

    # "I nearly dozed off again just watching."
    "Casi me vuelvo a quedar dormida solo mirando."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:48
translate spanish hwb_s23_cf52b836:

    # "Maybe someday, I’ll get to watch it with Marina. Someday, when I wake up early again, and if she manages to get her lazy ass out of bed."
    "Tal vez algún día, pueda verlo con Marina. Algún día, cuando me despierte temprano otra vez, y si ella logra sacar su perezoso trasero de la cama."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:52
translate spanish hwb_s23_c1f218ef:

    # "Lazy but cute."
    "Perezosa pero linda."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:54
translate spanish hwb_s23_3cc8fb26:

    # "Yesterday’s events replay in my mind for the umpteenth time. And with them come the swirl of emotions that feel like a stomachache and a high, both at once."
    "Los eventos de ayer se repiten en mi mente por enésima vez. Y con ellos llega el torbellino de emociones que se sienten como un dolor de estómago y un subidón, todo a la vez."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:56
translate spanish hwb_s23_72fa6591:

    # "Things finally starting to feel normal between us again."
    "Las cosas finalmente empiezan a sentirse normales entre nosotras otra vez."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:60
translate spanish hwb_s23_709277cc:

    # "Kissing Marina at the Valley of Fire."
    "Besar a Marina en el Valle de Fuego."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:62
translate spanish hwb_s23_624baa45:

    # "Her leaning into it."
    "Ella inclinándose hacia el beso."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:64
translate spanish hwb_s23_1cce229e:

    # "Wondering if I should stop."
    "Preguntándome si debería parar."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:66
translate spanish hwb_s23_b186f6ad:

    # "Her not letting me."
    "Ella no me deja."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:68
translate spanish hwb_s23_fbe4fe54:

    # "Sitting close on the couch, not asking any questions. Not answering them either."
    "Sentados cerca en el sofá, sin hacer preguntas. Sin responderlas tampoco."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:70
translate spanish hwb_s23_323790d3:

    # "Wondering if I should."
    "Preguntándome si debería."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:72
translate spanish hwb_s23_e9448d92:

    # "Ugh."
    "Uf."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:74
translate spanish hwb_s23_144daa2b:

    # "It’s too early for this shit."
    "Es demasiado temprano para esta mierda."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:76
translate spanish hwb_s23_12de0681:

    # "The familiar {i}ping{/i} of the coffee maker tells me that I’ve been zoned out for a few minutes now."
    "El familiar {i}ping{/i} de la cafetera me dice que he estado en las nubes por unos minutos."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:80
translate spanish hwb_s23_e936fb6d:

    # "Smashing my fists into my eyes, I try to rub the sleepiness out."
    "Apretando los puños contra mis ojos, intento frotar el sueño."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:82
translate spanish hwb_s23_b808c957:

    # "Movement from the back of the RV means that I must have woken Marina up. I can hear the sound of her bed creaking, and of the covers being thrown back."
    "Un movimiento desde el fondo de la casa rodante significa que debo haber despertado a Marina. Puedo oír el crujido de su cama y el sonido de las cobijas siendo apartadas."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:94
translate spanish hwb_s23_936403a2:

    # "I feel a strange, nervous elation as she appears in the hallway, looking bedraggled."
    "Siento una extraña y nerviosa emoción cuando aparece en el pasillo, luciendo desaliñada."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:100
translate spanish hwb_s23_c39b5768:

    # Amber "Good morning."
    Amber "Доброе утро."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:106
translate spanish hwb_s23_7a5334bd:

    # "She groans like a zombie and stumbles toward me."
    "Gime como un zombi y tropieza hacia mí."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:108
translate spanish hwb_s23_5964d92d:

    # Amber "Want some coffee?"
    Amber "Сделать тебе кофе?"

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:110
translate spanish hwb_s23_886a6bca:

    # "A stiff head nod."
    "Un movimiento de cabeza rígido."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:112
translate spanish hwb_s23_ccf6a8cc:

    # "Smiling, I prepare her a cup. It’s only half coffee. The other half is a boatload of sugar and the creamer that neither Gramps nor I ever drank."
    "Sonriendo, le preparo una taza. Es solo medio café. La otra mitad es un montón de azúcar y la crema que ni el Abuelo ni yo bebimos nunca."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:114
translate spanish hwb_s23_b94cd70e:

    # "I don’t even know why we had it, but it’s not expired."
    "Ni siquiera sé por qué la teníamos, pero no está caducada."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:122
translate spanish hwb_s23_da80f938:

    # "When she reaches me, Marina leans into me. Sort of falls, really, crashing against my shoulder."
    "Cuando llega a mí, Marina se apoya en mí. Como si se cayera, en realidad, estrellándose contra mi hombro."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:126
translate spanish hwb_s23_0db5643b:

    # Amber "Hey, careful."
    Amber "Хэй, аккуратнее."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:128
translate spanish hwb_s23_21eade32:

    # "A bit of coffee sloshes out of the mug and onto my hand, but I don’t mind. She takes the drink and a couple small sips."
    "Un poco de café se derrama de la taza y cae en mi mano, pero no me importa. Ella toma la bebida y da un par de sorbos pequeños."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:130
translate spanish hwb_s23_58fbf22b:

    # Marina "Mmmm."
    Marina "Ммм."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:132
translate spanish hwb_s23_ee7704c1:

    # "Minor bliss replaces her glazed expression."
    "Una dicha menor reemplaza su expresión vidriosa."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:134
translate spanish hwb_s23_bfa9ffb2:

    # Amber "Good?"
    Amber "Вкусный?"

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:136
translate spanish hwb_s23_6a4b3fd3:

    # Marina "Goooood."
    Marina "Вкуууусный."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:140
translate spanish hwb_s23_531eb9d9:

    # Amber "There’s hardly any coffee in it, you know."
    Amber "Ты же понимаешь, что там фактически нет самого кофе."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:142
translate spanish hwb_s23_1ebba4b3:

    # Marina "Just the way I like it."
    Marina "Как раз как я люблю."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:146
translate spanish hwb_s23_715fb476:

    # "I wonder if she had a hard time falling asleep like I did, but I’m hesitant to ask."
    "Me pregunto si le costó dormirse como a mí, pero dudo en preguntar."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:148
translate spanish hwb_s23_2536d1c2:

    # "Afraid she’d say no."
    "Miedo de que dijera que no."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:150
translate spanish hwb_s23_604ffe7c:

    # "Afraid she’d say yes."
    "Miedo de que dijera que sí."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:152
translate spanish hwb_s23_f96fef58:

    # "So I just sit down, and she takes a spot next to me. We both quietly sip our coffee as she rejoins the land of the living."
    "Así que solo me siento, y ella toma un lugar a mi lado. Ambas tomamos nuestro café en silencio mientras ella regresa al mundo de los vivos."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:154
translate spanish hwb_s23_706f3f28:

    # "Once she finishes her first cup, she’s alert enough for a conversation."
    "Una vez que termina su primera taza, está lo suficientemente alerta para una conversación."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:156
translate spanish hwb_s23_d509c06d:

    # Amber "Sleep okay?"
    Amber "Хорошо спала?"

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:158
translate spanish hwb_s23_62bd519d:

    # "I figure that’s safer than flat-out asking."
    "Supongo que eso es más seguro que preguntar directamente."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:162
translate spanish hwb_s23_e89cc3e6:

    # Marina "Mmm. Yeah, kinda."
    Marina "Ммм. Вроде того."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:166
translate spanish hwb_s23_2c02c7e6:

    # Amber "Kinda?"
    Amber "Вроде?"

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:170
translate spanish hwb_s23_fcaac16a:

    # Marina "I like…"
    Marina "Как будто…"

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:172
translate spanish hwb_s23_e0492165:

    # "She trails off. Maybe I gave her alertness too much credit."
    "Se queda en suspenso. Quizás le di demasiado crédito a su estado de alerta."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:176
translate spanish hwb_s23_3ccd5c1c:

    # Marina "I forgot what I was just saying."
    Marina "Я забыла, что хотела сказать."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:180
translate spanish hwb_s23_51daf26e:

    # "I laugh and stand up."
    "Me río y me levanto."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:182
translate spanish hwb_s23_5af58dc1:

    # Amber "Don’t worry about it."
    Amber "Не переживай из-за этого."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:186
translate spanish hwb_s23_57b79960:

    # "Marina mumbles something incoherent."
    "Marina murmura algo incoherente."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:190
translate spanish hwb_s23_7dacdc1c:

    # Amber "What was that?"
    Amber "Что это было?"

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:192
translate spanish hwb_s23_f50b9adc:

    # "She clears her throat."
    "Ella se aclara la garganta."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:196
translate spanish hwb_s23_01be9843:

    # Marina "Sorry. I asked if you slept alright."
    Marina "Извини. Я спрашивала, хорошо ли ты спала?"

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:200
translate spanish hwb_s23_9c7ffc4b:

    # Amber "Took me a while to fall asleep, but after that, yeah."
    Amber "Заняло немало времени, чтобы уснуть, но когда смогла - да."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:202
translate spanish hwb_s23_60c982ea:

    # "It’s not strictly a lie."
    "No es estrictamente una mentira."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:206
translate spanish hwb_s23_7708c979:

    # "Eyes half-closed, Marina smiles thinly."
    "Con los ojos entrecerrados, Marina sonríe débilmente."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:208
translate spanish hwb_s23_ffc9f18c:

    # Marina "Good."
    Marina "Хорошо."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:212
translate spanish hwb_s23_1543c9d6:

    # "I turn around so that she doesn’t see how preoccupied I am, or guess what’s on my mind."
    "Me doy la vuelta para que no vea lo preocupada que estoy, ni adivine lo que tengo en mente."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:214
translate spanish hwb_s23_723ecca9:

    # "Whatever it is that I’m dealing with, it’s not her problem."
    "Sea lo que sea lo que estoy enfrentando, no es su problema."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:216
translate spanish hwb_s23_6cc36e18:

    # "I don’t want her to worry about me."
    "No quiero que se preocupe por mí."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:218
translate spanish hwb_s23_28b59c09:

    # "The floor creaks as Marina stands up too, but I don’t face her."
    "El suelo cruje cuando Marina también se levanta, pero no la miro."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:222
translate spanish hwb_s23_77a49368:

    # Marina "So where are we going today?"
    Marina "И так, куда мы сегодня?"

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:226
translate spanish hwb_s23_417c8ce0:

    # Amber "No idea. We have a few days before the show. Anything you wanna see?"
    Amber "Без понятия. У нас есть пара дней до фестиваля. Хочешь что-нибудь посмотреть?"

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:228
translate spanish hwb_s23_9ea48544:

    # "Whatever it is, I’ll make the trip."
    "Sea lo que sea, haré el viaje."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:230
translate spanish hwb_s23_dd4d00f5:

    # Marina "We’re not very far from Las Vegas, right?"
    Marina "Мы же не далеко от Лас-Вегаса, правильно?"

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:234
translate spanish hwb_s23_2d433573:

    # Amber "Not at all. It’s just a couple hours."
    Amber "Не особо. Всего в паре часов езды."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:238
translate spanish hwb_s23_57f98f9c:

    # Marina "Let’s go there!"
    Marina "Ну тогда поехали!"

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:240
translate spanish hwb_s23_3c3c6ebd:

    # "Finally, I meet her eyes again. The smile on her face is pure and earnest. I can’t help but return it."
    "Finalmente, vuelvo a encontrarme con sus ojos. La sonrisa en su rostro es pura y sincera. No puedo evitar devolvérsela."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:242
translate spanish hwb_s23_82fea52d:

    # Amber "Sure. That sounds like fun."
    Amber "Конечно. Звучит весело."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:247
translate spanish hwb_s23_215c6b22:

    # "And she hugs me."
    "Y me abraza."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:249
translate spanish hwb_s23_37b21075:

    # "Her warm figure is pressed close against mine. She smells like my shampoo."
    "Su cálida figura se aprieta contra la mía. Huele a mi champú."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:251
translate spanish hwb_s23_3d1fb1ac:

    # "I wrap my arms around her and hold her close."
    "La envuelvo con mis brazos y la sostengo cerca."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:253
translate spanish hwb_s23_3423c508:

    # "Just for a second, everything feels right. Like it’s all gonna work out."
    "Solo por un segundo, todo se siente bien. Como si todo va a salir bien."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:255
translate spanish hwb_s23_90a08e90:

    # "And I realize how badly I want it to."
    "Y me doy cuenta de cuánto deseo que así sea."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:260
translate spanish hwb_s23_0faac395:

    # "I squeeze tight and then pull away."
    "La aprieto fuerte y luego me aparto."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:264
translate spanish hwb_s23_dc960a58:

    # Amber "What was that for?"
    Amber "Что это было?"

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:268
translate spanish hwb_s23_4f0fc5b7:

    # Marina "Just felt like it."
    Marina "Это были мои истинные чувства."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:272
translate spanish hwb_s23_626dbefb:

    # "Worry creases her face."
    "La preocupación arruga su rostro."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:274
translate spanish hwb_s23_ff04646a:

    # Marina "Should I not?"
    Marina "Мне не стоило?"

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:280
translate spanish hwb_s23_b2696db4:

    # Amber "Nah, you definitely should."
    Amber "Пф, конечно стоило."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:284
translate spanish hwb_s23_7db7c94c:

    # Amber "Go get dressed and I’ll get us on the road. You cool with waiting to eat until we get there?"
    Amber "Иди одевайся, а я пока выведу нас на дорогу. Ты же сможешь продержаться без еды до тех пор, пока мы не приедем?"

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:288
translate spanish hwb_s23_ca73936a:

    # Marina "Yeah!"
    Marina "Да!"

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:290
translate spanish hwb_s23_2ff766c7:

    # Amber "Cool. There are a million buffets and exotic restaurants there, so we can find something good."
    Amber "Клево. Там миллионы забегаловок и разных экзотических ресторанов, так что мы сможем хорошо поесть."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:294
translate spanish hwb_s23_083963a0:

    # Marina "I like Las Vegas already."
    Marina "Мне уже нравится Лас-Вегас."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:298
translate spanish hwb_s23_c8ff6963:

    # Amber "Dork."
    Amber "Ну ты и глупыш."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:300
translate spanish hwb_s23_75c935fa:

    # "I gently push her towards the back to go get ready. She sticks her tongue out over her shoulder as she goes."
    "La empujo suavemente hacia la parte de atrás para que se aliste. Saca la lengua por encima del hombro mientras se va."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:337
translate spanish hwb_s23_2094617f:

    # "Watching, I rub my temple before climbing into the front seat."
    "Mirándola, me froto la sien antes de subirme al asiento delantero."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:339
translate spanish hwb_s23_c09f30b3:

    # "I’m looking forward to this, and I know Marina is too."
    "Estoy deseando esto, y sé que Marina también."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:341
translate spanish hwb_s23_e3465d61:

    # "So why does it feel like I’m doing something wrong?"
    "Entonces, ¿por qué se siente como si estuviera haciendo algo malo?"

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:351
translate spanish hwb_s23_91913fbb:

    # "For a long moment, I just press my forehead against the steering wheel, not thinking much of anything. The sound of Marina’s approaching footsteps makes me sit up, and I put on a smile as she hops into her spot."
    "Por un largo momento, solo presiono mi frente contra el volante, sin pensar en mucho. El sonido de los pasos de Marina acercándose me hace enderezarme, y pongo una sonrisa mientras ella salta a su lugar."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:355
translate spanish hwb_s23_373fa4e6:

    # Amber "Ready?"
    Amber "Готова?"

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:359
translate spanish hwb_s23_aaa9bcf8:

    # Marina "Yep!"
    Marina "Ага!"

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:363
translate spanish hwb_s23_33131cfa:

    # Amber "Here we go, then."
    Amber "Ну тогда вперед."

# game/script/hwb_s23.rpy:365
translate spanish hwb_s23_e0e54657:

    # "And we head out towards the highway."
    "Y nos dirigimos hacia la carretera."

translate spanish strings:

    # script/hwb_s23.rpy:392
    old "Driving to Las Vegas"
    new "Driving to Las Vegas"

